---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Preventative Dental Care in Footscray | Expert Check-Ups, Cleanings, and Plaque Control"
  description="Ensure lifelong dental health with our preventative care services at Top Dentists Footscray. Our expert dentists and hygienists provide thorough check-ups, professional cleanings, and plaque control to help you avoid cavities and maintain a healthy smile."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Preventative Care</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Preventative Care
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Prevention is always better than cure and it is now possible to grow up without needing a filling. The key to avoiding problems and maintaining excellent dental health is the control of dental plaque. Professional check up and cleans are performed by our qualified dentists or oral hygienists.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Your cleaning appointment will include a dental exam and the following:
            </p>

            <!-- Services Details -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Removal of calculus (tartar)</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Removal of hardened plaque that has been left on the tooth for some time and is firmly attached to the tooth surface. Calculus forms above and below the gum line and can only be removed with special dental instruments.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Removal of plaque</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Plaque is a sticky, almost invisible film that forms on the teeth. It is a growing colony of living bacteria, food debris, and saliva. The bacteria produce toxins (poisons) that inflame the gums.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Teeth polishing</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Removal of stain and plaque that is not otherwise removed during tooth brushing and scaling.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Additional Information -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                White Composite Fillings
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                Fillings are sometimes necessary. A white composite filling is used to repair a tooth that is affected by decay, cracks, fractures, etc. The decayed or affected portion of the tooth will be removed and then filled. Because composite fillings are white, they can be closely matched to the colour of existing teeth. Composites are very durable and will last many years, giving you a long lasting, beautiful smile.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits Section -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Benefits of Preventative Care
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Prevents cavities and tooth decay</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Early detection of dental issues</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Maintains healthy gums</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Fresh breath and clean feeling</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Recommended Frequency
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    Every 6 months
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    Regular check-ups and cleans help maintain optimal oral health and catch any issues early.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready for Your Preventative Care?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          To organise an appointment please call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          or press here to book online
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>